 runs Native Image with `Preserve` and `TrackDynamicAccess`, and prints a JSON summary suitable for issue comments.\\n\\n### Generating Metadata\\n\\nGenerates metadata for a single library coordinate. If `agentAllowedPackages` is provided, a new user-code-filter.json will be created or updated from those packages or from package roots derived from the resolved library JAR.\\n\\n- `coordinates`: group:artifact:version (single coordinate only)\\n- `agentAllowedPackages`: comma-separated package list, `fromJar`, or `-` for none\\n\\nExamples:\\n   ```console\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=org.example.app,com.acme.service\\n\\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777294974878}]}\n370:  ./metadata/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/reachability-metadata.json\n384:  ./metadata/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/reachability-metadata.json\n399:  ./metadata/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/reachability-metadata.json\n407:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_FqgkWYMe0D8UrOJPhJfWYrkF|fc_045546e01dc4431b0169ef5e82e1c881a0a4dcb01199108d08\", \"toolName\": \"bash\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"./build/agent-artifact-discovery-logs/cglib-cglib-nodep-2.2.2.log\\n./build/agent-url-discovery-logs/cglib-cglib-nodep-2.2.2.log\\n./build/discovered-artifact-metadata/cglib-cglib-nodep-2.2.2.json\\n./build/tests/cglib:cglib-nodep:2.2.2/53027d73ec7ce20850b898e070a4f852.out\\n./build/tests/cglib:cglib-nodep:2.2.2/561169cc4cebcc950bde480b0c3a0e5e.out\\n./build/tests/cglib:cglib-nodep:2.2.2/af413ea432946bce897d0c40de1cda7f.out\\n./metadata/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/reachability-metadata.json\\n./metadata/cglib/cglib-nodep/index.json